title: welcome
description: Welcome to Project EDDIE Module 6 'Ecological Forecast Uncertainty' R Shiny App!

title: tab_nav1
description: Navigate through the module by selecting a tab.

title: tab_nav2
description: Or you can use these buttons at the bottom of the page to also navigate through the tabs.

title: objectives
description: There are objectives on each of the tabs. You will need to complete them sequentially.

title: questions
description: Questions are embedded throughout the app. Answer as you go and they will be included in your final report. You can resize the text boxes by clicking and dragging the bottom right corner.

title: finish
description: When you are finished you can generate a Word document with your answers and plots embedded which you can then download.

title: help
description: If you require any further help you can use the help button in the top right corner.

title: start
description: Start from here and make sure to read through all the text carefully and answer the questions as you go.
